reviews.review_text: Saint Paul 73' This is an excellent show from an amazing year.Perfect song selection,very well played.I'm a huge 73' fan and this hits the sweet spot.Thanks for the upgrade Charlie and thanks for what you do o to keep the music alive as it's greatly appreciated.
